        <ab>mattu tōṇṭavuṁ<g type="danda">.</g></ab>
        <ab>nandanavanamuṁ sarbbabādhāparihāraṁ<g type="danda">.</g></ab>
        <ab>pañca maṭhasthānamam <lb n="32"></lb> pūrva-maryādeyoḷ-vr̥tti-pāḷisuvudu<g type="danda">.</g></ab>
        <ab>mūṟu-baravuvilla-mūrmmane-vārtegara mane pokkaḍe manneraḍu gadyāṇa daṇḍa<g type="danda">.</g></ab>
        <p>haradarakka <lb break="no" n="33"></lb>naṁgadoḷvāradarigeya paccavaṁ-koṇḍu pādarigeya mūganaridu pādarigaganaṁ kolvaru<g type="danda">.</g></p>
